  "detailed_description": "A creative aquarium simulation and management game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Species</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/df83ed7d1a86690b59fb54a5a70c425e.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>Almost all the fish and plants that are in the game are created to imitate their real life counterparts. The art style of the game is very stylistic but we aim to make every species recognizable to people familiar with the hobby.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dimorphism</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/5772b45ea83a667505e8a3afb4cd9acc.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>Quite often male and female fish of particular species have differences in their body shape and colour patterns. It is important to us that we show this in game even when the differences between male and female are very subtle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Creativity</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/b497477275eea3fa47e99b2f04171875.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>Every aquarium can tell a story. Create dramatic rocky landscapes, thick aquatic jungle or even a scene showing the rusting carcass of a sunken machine. It's up to you to create the unique world that your fish inhabit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shrimp</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/2fd791efef943253bf6ef910c17a5f93.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>It is not only fish that can live in an aquarium. Populate your ecosystems with animals that crawl as well as swim.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lighting</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/b4077005e0aeb41789854e51431b2d93.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>Create a sense of mystery, awe, curiosity or just simple fun with our simple but powerful lighting tools.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Substrate</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/b16efdade5764264724e67b1ab1beb7d.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>The substrate is an important part of any aquarium. It can be sculpted to make a dramatic landscape for fish and plants to inhabit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Backdrops</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/b4521b25013900e6e182b81c568a63b7.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>The environment that your aquarium sits in can be key to bringing your creative vision to life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Breeding</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/cc2a338786e8bec2c705bb985f763283.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>You will know if your fish are happy and contented in the habitat you have created for them because they will have lots of babies.",
  "about_the_game": "A creative aquarium simulation and management game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Species</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/df83ed7d1a86690b59fb54a5a70c425e.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>Almost all the fish and plants that are in the game are created to imitate their real life counterparts. The art style of the game is very stylistic but we aim to make every species recognizable to people familiar with the hobby.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dimorphism</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/5772b45ea83a667505e8a3afb4cd9acc.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>Quite often male and female fish of particular species have differences in their body shape and colour patterns. It is important to us that we show this in game even when the differences between male and female are very subtle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Creativity</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/b497477275eea3fa47e99b2f04171875.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>Every aquarium can tell a story. Create dramatic rocky landscapes, thick aquatic jungle or even a scene showing the rusting carcass of a sunken machine. It's up to you to create the unique world that your fish inhabit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shrimp</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/2fd791efef943253bf6ef910c17a5f93.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>It is not only fish that can live in an aquarium. Populate your ecosystems with animals that crawl as well as swim.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Lighting</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/b4077005e0aeb41789854e51431b2d93.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>Create a sense of mystery, awe, curiosity or just simple fun with our simple but powerful lighting tools.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Substrate</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/b16efdade5764264724e67b1ab1beb7d.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>The substrate is an important part of any aquarium. It can be sculpted to make a dramatic landscape for fish and plants to inhabit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Backdrops</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/b4521b25013900e6e182b81c568a63b7.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>The environment that your aquarium sits in can be key to bringing your creative vision to life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Breeding</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/809730/extras/cc2a338786e8bec2c705bb985f763283.avif?t=1772135148\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>You will know if your fish are happy and contented in the habitat you have created for them because they will have lots of babies.",
